  <div class="modal" id="centredIconModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="centredIconModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title" id="centredIconModalLabel">Objectif de la modale</h5>
          <button type="button" class="btn-close close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
            {{> styles-icon-item("icon-name": "icon-x")}}
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body text-center">
          <div class="modal-icon">
            <span class="icon icon-sante-et-securite-publiques" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="h3">Titre</h2>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent egestas enim nec erat vulputate, at luctus neque lacinia. Phasellus sed ex ultrices, faucibus nisl sit amet, tincidunt magna.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-tertiary">Annuler</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Action</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
